After the weapon is enhanced, it will take effect immediately (only effective in the current Tigerstorm), the critical hit rate of the attack will be increased to AA, Strengthening the weapon requires CC costume fragments.
Each purchase of a Tigerstorm portrait frame will grant 1 attack.

Using weapons to attack tiger consumes a lot of physical strength. Each attack consumes 10 (HP)physical strength. If the physical strength is insufficient, you cannot attack. When the physical strength value is lower than AA, you can recover physical strength every time. You can gain physical strength by sacrificing coins. For every BB coins sacrificed, you can gain 10 (HP)physical strength.
The top ten users on the Trial Ranking will be given the right to give AA gifts. Please give in the gift column.
After the weapon is upgraded, it will take effect immediately. Each attack will gain AA trial points, and there is a BB chance of gaining CC to DD trial points.
The top ten users on the Trial Ranking will be given the right to give AA gifts. Please give in the gift column.
Each attack consumes 10 HP (regardless of the number of attacks)

1. Activity is open from 19:00 to 20:00 every night. Due to the instability of the space rift, tiger will only last for 60 minutes and will return to its space after 60 minutes.
 2. During the trial, all platform users can use weapons to attack tiger, causing 10 damage to it, and gain 10 trial value at the same time, with a 5% chance of critical hit to gain 10-15 trial value.
 3. Each person has 100 HP(strength) by default. Each attack (regardless of the number of combos, 100 combos are also considered as an attack) consumes 10 physical strength. If the physical strength is not enough, the weapon cannot be
 controlled to attack. After the physical strength is lower than 100, rest for 30 seconds to restore 10 HP(strength). The upper limit of physical strength for each person is 100 physical strength, and the physical strength can only be restored during the Tigerstorm.
 4. After the tiger is defeated, it will leave treasures. The top three on the spot will receive mysterious high-value gifts.
 5. When the blood volume of tiger is exhausted by the attack, it will flee the continent and wait for the next reappearance.
 6. The trial value obtained by all people in the platform attacking tiger will be recorded every day and announced on the trial ranking. The list will be reset to zero at midnight. After the reset, the top ten on the previous day is list will receive mysterious high-value gifts.
 7. There is a chance to get fragments when attacking tiger. The obtained fragments can be redeemed for limited gifts by clicking [Exchange Shop].
 8. Attacking tiger may randomly drop costume fragments. You can click [Exchange Shop] to exchange the obtained costume fragments for limited costumes. They can also be used to strengthen weapons and obtain more trial points.
 9.This event has nothing to do with Apple and Google.
